<div id="Content">
<h2><a href="courses/intro2ict/index.html">Introduction to Information &amp; Communication Technology</a></h2>

<p>Introduction to Information and Communication Technology is a foundations
course for everyone who is <q>interested in computers</q>. The course is
designed to both orient students to the field of Information and Communication
Technology, while at the same time helping them build core competencies that
will be needed for higher-level study in the field.</p>
</div>

